{"id":23454,"date":"2024-02-14T18:38:39","date_gmt":"2021-07-14T13:08:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=23454"},"modified":"2022-05-31T11:21:07","modified_gmt":"2022-05-31T05:51:07","slug":"asian-style-interior-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/asian-style-interior-design\/","title":{"rendered":"Stunning Asian-Style Interior Design Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Wondering how to incorporate Asian-style interior design in your Indian home? Here are some tips to help you get started<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each continent of the world is a melting pot of cultures, and along with it, they bring a plethora of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a> ideas worth stealing. One such inspirational style is the Asian interior design space. Inspired to evoke a sense of tranquillity and calm, Asian interiors are perfect for today\u2019s fast-paced, rat-race lifestyle. The image of a home that drives one to sit back with family and immerse in harmony has Asian elements at its core. Here how you can incorporate oriental touches into your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home\u2019s interior design<\/a> while keeping the space refreshingly welcoming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Asian Interior Design For Living Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An amalgamation of classic silhouettes and soothing colours, this Asian-inspired living room is one to bookmark. The use of soft hues with bold blacks brings out an outward charm to the home, while the calming yellow lights diffuse warmth even in the corners. A bespoke mustard yellow sofa suffuses the room with energy and the brightly coloured ceramic pot ups the tempo in the home. Small decor accents like an abstract figurine painting and faux greens scattered across the room infuse a Zen ambience into the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183114\/asian-interior-design-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Asian style living room design with a yellow sofa and yellow lights brings out an outward charm.\" class=\"wp-image-23455\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183114\/asian-interior-design-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183114\/asian-interior-design-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183114\/asian-interior-design-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183114\/asian-interior-design-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Asian-inspired interior designs for homes rarely shy away from colour. A bright emerald green sofa will also look highly versatile in the living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Asian-Inspired Interior Design For Bedrooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Inspired by the colours of nature, this Asian-style bedroom reinterprets the beauty and calmness of the landscape outside. The room\u2019s backdrop is a focal point that offers a soothing and relaxed ambience to the space. Painted in soft hues of sage green, the gentle aesthetics of the room mimic a mess-free Asian home. Contributing to the mystical earthy charm is a large window that allows the flow of natural light, keeping your personal space well-ventilated and airy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183133\/asian-interior-style-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom in asian interior style with a brick wall in sage green and indoor plants lends a soothing and relaxed vibe.\" class=\"wp-image-23458\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183133\/asian-interior-style-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183133\/asian-interior-style-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183133\/asian-interior-style-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183133\/asian-interior-style-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The use of luscious green plants within a home is an integral part of Asian-style interior design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Asian-Style Interiors With Vivacious Colours<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, Asian interior design often uses vibrant hues that stand out in a sea of colours. This stunning room is the perfect balance of mystic charm and spellbinding elegance. A lustrous deep blue backdrop with exquisite gold tones creates an opulent room where you will enjoy every nap you take. Complementing the bold blue is a soft blush pink bed set that makes a trendy style statement in itself. The harmony of different textures and colours is what binds this Asian-style home in a poised fashion.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183127\/asian-interior-design-style-with-vivacious-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Asian style bedroom design with a lustrous deep blue backdrop with exquisite gold tones.\" class=\"wp-image-23457\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183127\/asian-interior-design-style-with-vivacious-colours.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183127\/asian-interior-design-style-with-vivacious-colours-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183127\/asian-interior-design-style-with-vivacious-colours-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183127\/asian-interior-design-style-with-vivacious-colours-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>our home is more than bricks and cement. It is a representation of your vibrant dreams and personal style<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Asian-Style Interiors Beyond Visual Boundaries<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who said your interior design ideas must be limited to the core areas of your home? This Asian-inspired bathroom creates an atmosphere of simplicity and ease. A vibrant maroon with white is considered lucky in Asian cultures, while gold fixtures are a modern-day style statement to make within your home. An elegant white bathtub calls out to you after an exhausting day as you unwind your worries and gear up refreshed for a new day. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/brick-wall-designs\/\">brick-style wall<\/a> adds a rustic appeal to the space in a sculpturally appealing way.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183138\/bathroom-in-asian-interior-style.jpg\" alt=\"Asian style bathroom design in vibrant maroon with white colour and brick-style wall adds a rustic appeal.\" class=\"wp-image-23459\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183138\/bathroom-in-asian-interior-style.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183138\/bathroom-in-asian-interior-style-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183138\/bathroom-in-asian-interior-style-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183138\/bathroom-in-asian-interior-style-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>If you are looking to add fluidity to the room, a pair of wall lights diffusing a warm yellow glow will fill the space with positivity and peace<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Fusion Of Asian Zen Interior Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your balcony can be fashioned in Asian-style interiors. Not your traditional outdoor space, this home dons a fusion theme of several styles. A simple Japanese-style enclosed balcony transforms into a cosy work-from-home space. Minimalistic and close to nature, this fusion interior design style adds the perfect amount of Zen to your home. When you\u2019re not working, you can enjoy a hot cappuccino overlooking the skyline of your city or cosy up with your pet and enjoy a lazy Sunday.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183144\/fusion-of-asian-zen-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Balcony in asian zen interior design with wood as a backdrop on the wall adds the perfect amount of Zen.\" class=\"wp-image-23460\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183144\/fusion-of-asian-zen-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183144\/fusion-of-asian-zen-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183144\/fusion-of-asian-zen-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14183144\/fusion-of-asian-zen-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The use of wood as a backdrop on the wall and neat tiles on the floor is a fusion of two distinct cultures: Indian and pan-Asian<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Asian interior designs are more than mere fashion statements, and that is the beauty of it. Thinking beyond the decor itself, Asian-themed homes are sustainable and involve eco-friendly building materials. The use of natural materials and earthy colours transforms a modern home into a serene space. Clean, well-defined textures and minimalistic decor are a natural part of Asian-style interior designs. The secret behind creating a Zen home is to surround yourself with things you absolutely love and those that spark joy. If you are not too sure on how to go the Asian route, we at Design Cafe can help you make small but permanent changes for a more tranquil home right in the middle of your city bustle!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/zen-interior-design-ideas\/\">Zen Interior Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <inp